  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c9fc137b-2583-4ce1-8fe1-f39194e414bd\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-33027aec-285e-4da3-a8c6-9a7426766bd3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-64eb94a5-66fc-4460-8e02-424f8768531b\"><b>안녕하세요! 사당동한의원 </b></span><span style=\"background-color:#98d36c;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-11b8d3c9-0eda-4d25-a871-811089157c9d\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-72ee2ce4-75e1-4e9f-894b-e46afeeb7c6e\"><b>입니다!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-c9fc137b-2583-4ce1-8fe1-f39194e414bd\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1ab4df8d-401e-4ddd-aade-935f8963cec0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"2\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_2.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6b694ed3-be15-49df-a466-5d34b8a7eda7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fbb593d2-3257-40e9-8a8f-877d99a94dee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-842a685f-a75b-425f-b7b0-7814849eca90\"><b>이수한의원의 두통 맞춤 한방처방</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-36247214-cc9e-4e5d-900a-58f74b81d7de\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b6662101-0c96-42ca-be2b-66965d20ff90\">두통, 참는다고 해결되지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c3c5f055-a7ca-4083-b997-fdf79412bfb4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6920d676-b733-4a63-b6f4-6fb206450699\">같은 두통이라도 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-849102db-9172-4692-9943-6aab3cb22a61\"><b>‘어디가 아픈지’</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-778a995f-e80a-4e1c-b699-e50d490464d8\">, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b14a090f-a046-48a4-aea5-a69228a25f67\"><b>‘어떨 때 생기는지’</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-76f3e449-80cd-4cec-bd02-67597e7532a3\">, ‘어떤 체질인지’에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-517cbde3-241b-49a6-b719-c068b809e51c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3d03f361-7a0b-4d47-b113-323165416367\">따라 원인도, 치료도 달라집니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2844f53b-4883-4cdf-88dd-c2b362d0e6ed\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-11580c12-e7c8-4676-b084-287946d4e5bc\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-94dec7c0-e9df-4bab-b684-a2a3571ff828\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3474f647-3080-42d9-8b9b-6fa17f0ce2e6\">이수한의원에서는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d95abcf5-ad54-4add-9d7c-4d410e2f084b\"><b>두통의 위치와 원인에 따라 체질에 맞는 한방 처방</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b88d5350-0e2e-401d-8e4c-6d55df1bde46\">을 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b316937e-7fb8-4538-92b2-e0c0c7205465\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e0118768-00ef-48c9-a9b3-54bf0b021b1d\">제안합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-6b694ed3-be15-49df-a466-5d34b8a7eda7\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-03a1787d-159c-4725-8907-deedf9bc49ae\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f211e2ba-37db-4758-92ff-716417618eb0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f211e2ba-37db-4758-92ff-716417618eb0\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a3cf62e87e56283d.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1400\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1400\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a3cf62e87e56283d.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a3cf62e87e56283d.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-f211e2ba-37db-4758-92ff-716417618eb0\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ffbc6226-1c0c-47ef-9daa-12c965a1c2fa\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-81e42b64-1920-4e53-bf2e-9ffe99a271e1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d1de8b56-076b-4622-988e-cbe89d877bfd\"><b>✔ 어떤 위치가 아프신가요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-08491ae3-afec-4251-b9d6-6b15d7ebe18f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e7e4a98b-f324-49a6-9467-8105b1ef076c\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-db965fdf-c8e5-47c3-b79f-3ae08357ad43\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9723ee97-b3c3-47f8-a386-bbbb8ae10bc7\"><b>① 이마가 띵하고 아픈 경우</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ae80dfb2-c8d9-491b-9d84-e2ab44009c38\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7f34b31e-75fb-49c2-8498-9d683bafbbf4\">주로 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9638e9f5-aff4-48a1-8af6-8fb54938e4bb\"><b>열이 위로 올라와서 생기는 두통</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4c6681ad-0873-45c6-8685-472b5032acb4\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1959b393-448b-4a77-8f30-f7ad660c9a9e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d0d34fe9-d958-4414-8d83-46178930e566\">스트레스를 받거나 잠을 못 잤을 때 자주 나타나며, 얼굴이 붉어지고 열이 날 수 있어요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c400e6dc-fa8e-4de1-9e38-631e7fb7affe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e06ad698-8b44-4ab9-baee-b8d4f21c7286\"><b>소양인에게 자주 나타나는 유형</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dbf88da1-37e1-4e5b-863a-7b44eaac804e\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3c23a312-b5ab-42e6-8551-3957741f8083\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-99466950-d5c0-4495-92ed-3575b6c8d68d\">▶ </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f3d59072-67db-4624-bd2c-7701755c976c\"><b>한방치료 포인트</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8097ad1e-ef5a-49e0-aff9-1a0435c0a51c\">: 열을 내려주고 머리를 맑게 해주는 처방과 침치료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-38cd8bc6-2fd4-4423-a58a-2f809d948d7f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-15d6d6e5-8694-4adf-8dcb-655bfe4eb48e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d353ee2e-8e86-44c9-95da-b6f2a38edcda\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6fe9c99c-ef95-4196-a932-7bc2bc68506f\"><b>② 머리 전체가 꽉 조이는 듯한 통증</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-974ef047-eb44-4f15-ab5a-08d5cb8701db\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-da644647-6648-4893-be88-3af966fdc893\"><b>스트레스로 인한 긴장성 두통</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-08f6a1a0-5a58-421a-a9a7-ec8e6255cf63\">일 가능성이 높습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0b056679-b00c-4ac0-8244-ae527ddaf65d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d6b85f70-2a8a-4ac5-a538-ec39514de042\">컴퓨터 앞에서 장시간 업무를 하거나, 걱정이 많을 때 자주 생깁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9a137c53-4e34-4def-a7a9-db939baf8ade\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-15a665a5-d7d3-44f4-a491-b600bd002974\">어깨나 목이 뻣뻣하게 느껴질 수도 있어요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-be2d756e-62a1-412e-a412-b962eaa802c1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d5e15190-3e83-46e5-9b43-451193bf581f\">▶ </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3661d003-0fc9-41c4-a922-2bc68fb7c69c\"><b>한방치료 포인트</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-22fb1c59-8299-428b-8035-9bb017ca557c\">: 기혈순환을 도와주는 침·뜸 치료, 마음 안정 처방</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b354bf76-1917-4dce-91ee-21f368ea2632\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-44656384-9e7f-45dc-9374-a3b3d5aeb044\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b77c9d38-3f4d-4bb7-b854-b0f60742de1c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fb9107b5-285b-41b3-8898-745a8e7c1544\"><b>③ 뒷머리가 무겁고 당기는 느낌</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6419b689-09d7-4b21-abd3-ea0811193d86\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5fcf0ba4-3066-4335-948b-68a51cc553f2\"><b>몸이 찬 사람에게 자주 나타나는 두통</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3f78569d-af17-4130-ac20-a11cc6d45a1b\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a5d399cd-f241-48d2-b361-ac66bffe094d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c2f4d4f1-123a-4d02-b984-98377d1a17ff\">날씨가 추워지면 더 심해지고, 피로하거나 감기 기운 있을 때 두통이 생기기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f2474251-08e5-421b-8ee4-1f52047e3282\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a71564fd-987e-4155-91de-dcfa8c929f94\"><b>소음인 체질에서 많이 나타납니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-20c0ece7-5384-4fd9-999a-6478a3fd925e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0e8bb17f-7820-45ab-bfcc-7835c40e66ad\">▶ </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5d4981e1-b6cb-4b9c-ae16-8eeff4a0ab73\"><b>한방치료 포인트</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-26f3e3cb-cfc3-4ee6-8fe4-6b538baf74cc\">: 몸을 따뜻하게 하고, 순환을 도와주는 처방과 뜸치료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-24bf27f5-019f-4a70-b74f-69d62a7d4451\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-55210843-e8d5-4293-8b46-4350cca84388\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-42e53a53-4771-4c13-986c-f7402db22941\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2315e9d3-05f7-4a0b-880f-d130b840ca08\"><b>④ 머리가 묵직하고 멍한 느낌</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e952e952-041f-4f5a-8c73-93a21a322c4c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cba34541-681b-4fe0-a464-3081b631b0d0\">두피 전체가 눌린 듯하고 머리가 무겁다면,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-77a2ccd4-ac08-42d8-83e6-8bac90610f42\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-379494e0-5bab-40a3-aba5-8d319710fbf1\"><b>소화기능이 떨어졌거나 몸 안에 습기가 많은 상태</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-38f6544c-594e-49ae-bb90-22170446bfa1\">일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5ba10d0d-f1e9-4d1f-9fb3-8927e5a49f9d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-82c386be-946c-40d4-8e0c-7b32fc57c059\">기운이 없고 몸도 자주 붓는 분들에게 자주 생깁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6f5e5ab6-4205-4bf8-ac09-9e30ae747500\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-50bf37bb-5387-43b2-ae05-a747cf587282\">▶ </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6af0a357-6a56-4217-ace3-bd492deac356\"><b>한방치료 포인트</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b90c50de-adc6-4054-8eed-6d223586a20a\">: 위장을 다스리고, 몸 안 습기를 줄이는 한약과 침치료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-ffbc6226-1c0c-47ef-9daa-12c965a1c2fa\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-807d3923-d6bb-42ef-96e1-c74b0780170e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-807d3923-d6bb-42ef-96e1-c74b0780170e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b27f6f1ece9a8d8e.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1536\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b27f6f1ece9a8d8e.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b27f6f1ece9a8d8e.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"750\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n         